cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper discusses interpretability and stability of deep neural networks in the context of image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also touches upon the issue of model robustness, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
